[This post][1] is not actual any more, so here is another solution:

&nbsp;

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="http://nexusnotes.ru/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Снимок-экрана-2012-07-27-в-10.57.22-3.png"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-924" title="Снимок экрана 2012-07-27 в 10.57.22 3" src="http://nexusnotes.ru/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Снимок-экрана-2012-07-27-в-10.57.22-3.png" alt="" width="400" height="412" /></a>
</p>

Go to  ~/Library/Preferences/

Open com.apple.iChat.AIM.plist

Change ForceICQPlainText to true

Save, put read-only attribute on file

Logoff/logon. Enjoy.

